### Moderation API V2 Test Calls
### Base URL: http://localhost/admin/v2
### Replace <user_id> and <status_id> with actual values

@base_url = http://localhost/admin/v2
@user_id = 1
@project_id = 1
@status_id = 1

### 1. Create a new moderation request (Application Access Request)
POST {{base_url}}/moderation_status/administration/{{user_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue_type": "application_access_request",
  "project_id": {{project_id}},
  "entity_id": 42,
  "description": "I need this application for my data analysis work. My team requires access to perform quarterly reports."
}

### 2. Create a pending request (default status)
POST {{base_url}}/moderation_status/administration/{{user_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue_type": "application_access_request",
  "project_id": {{project_id}},
  "entity_id": 43,
  "description": "Need access to integrate with our analytics pipeline",
  "meta": {
    "requested_by_team": "Data Science",
    "priority": "high"
  }
}

### 3. Create a feature request
POST {{base_url}}/moderation_status/administration/{{user_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue_type": "feature_request",
  "project_id": {{project_id}},
  "description": "Request to add export functionality for reports",
  "meta": {
    "feature_category": "reporting",
    "estimated_users": 50
  }
}

### 4. Get all requests for a user
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_status/administration/{{user_id}}

### 5. Get user's requests filtered by issue type
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_status/administration/{{user_id}}?issue_type=application_access_request

### 6. Get user's requests filtered by project
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_status/administration/{{user_id}}?project_id={{project_id}}

### 7. Get user's requests filtered by entity
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_status/administration/{{user_id}}?entity_id=42

### 8. List all moderation requests (paginated)
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_statuses/administration?limit=10&offset=0

### 9. List pending requests
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_statuses/administration?status=pending&limit=20

### 10. List application access requests
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_statuses/administration?issue_type=application_access_request

### 11. List requests for a specific project
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_statuses/administration?project_id={{project_id}}

### 12. List requests with multiple filters
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_statuses/administration?status=pending&issue_type=application_access_request&project_id={{project_id}}

### 13. Search by user ID
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_statuses/administration?search={{user_id}}

### 14. List with custom sorting (newest first)
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_statuses/administration?sort_by=created_at&sort_order=desc

### 15. List with custom sorting (oldest first)
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_statuses/administration?sort_by=created_at&sort_order=asc

### 16. Approve a request
PUT {{base_url}}/moderation_status/administration/{{user_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": {{status_id}},
  "status": "approved"
}

### 17. Reject a request with comment
PUT {{base_url}}/moderation_status/administration/{{user_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": {{status_id}},
  "status": "rejected",
  "rejection_comment": "Missing compliance training. Please complete the required XYZ certification course before requesting access."
}

### 18. Reject with detailed guidance
PUT {{base_url}}/moderation_status/administration/{{user_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": {{status_id}},
  "status": "rejected",
  "rejection_comment": "Request denied due to: 1) Missing manager approval 2) Incomplete justification 3) Need to specify data access requirements. Please resubmit with complete information."
}

### 19. Update metadata only
PUT {{base_url}}/moderation_status/administration/{{user_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": {{status_id}},
  "meta": {
    "reviewed_by": "admin@example.com",
    "review_date": "2026-05-21",
    "notes": "Approved after verification"
  }
}

### 20. Update rejection comment
PUT {{base_url}}/moderation_status/administration/{{user_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": {{status_id}},
  "rejection_comment": "Updated: Please contact security@example.com for access approval process"
}

### 21. List approved requests
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_statuses/administration?status=approved

### 22. List rejected requests
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_statuses/administration?status=rejected

### 23. Pagination - Page 1
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_statuses/administration?limit=5&offset=0

### 24. Pagination - Page 2
GET {{base_url}}/moderation_statuses/administration?limit=5&offset=5

### 25. Test validation error - missing required fields
POST {{base_url}}/moderation_status/administration/{{user_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue_type": "application_access_request"
}

### 26. Test validation error - invalid status
POST {{base_url}}/moderation_status/administration/{{user_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue_type": "test",
  "project_id": {{project_id}},
  "description": "test",
  "status": "invalid_status"
}

### 27. Test validation error - reject without comment
PUT {{base_url}}/moderation_status/administration/{{user_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": {{status_id}},
  "status": "rejected"
}
